title: BlackIsBetter - Kases (Cup of Sugar) NEW 30 May 2018
description: Kali is having a wild night in her kitchen—dancing and baking up a storm. She’s got the music jacked and not a care in the world. That is, until her neighbor, Isiah, stops by to ask her to turn down the music. At first, she’s happy to placate him but she quickly decides she doesn’t care if he’s bothered—she has a right to have fun in her own place. Plus, she’s willing to tolerate the wrath of a surly neighbor, especially when he’s as hot as Isiah.
